      <title>Array 对象</title>
      <link>/posts/88/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Sep 2022 09:00:29 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/posts/88/</guid>
      <description>创建特定数组的副本 复制特定数组实例，可以通过 of() 或 valueOf() 来实现。
let array01 = Array.of(1, &amp;#39;two&amp;#39;, 3, &amp;#39;four&amp;#39;, 5, &amp;#39;six&amp;#39;); let array02 = [1, &amp;#39;two&amp;#39;, 3, &amp;#39;four&amp;#39;, 5, &amp;#39;six&amp;#39;]; let array03 = Array(1, &amp;#39;two&amp;#39;, 3, &amp;#39;four&amp;#39;, 5, &amp;#39;six&amp;#39;); let array04 = new Array(1, &amp;#39;two&amp;#39;, 3, &amp;#39;four&amp;#39;, 5, &amp;#39;six&amp;#39;); console.log(array01); // [1, &amp;#34;two&amp;#34;, 3, &amp;#34;four&amp;#34;, 5, &amp;#34;six&amp;#34;] console.log(array02); // [1, &amp;#34;two&amp;#34;, 3, &amp;#34;four&amp;#34;, 5, &amp;#34;six&amp;#34;] console.log(array03); // [1, &amp;#34;two&amp;#34;, 3, &amp;#34;four&amp;#34;, 5, &amp;#34;six&amp;#34;] console.log(array04); // [1, &amp;#34;two&amp;#34;, 3, &amp;#34;four&amp;#34;, 5, &amp;#34;six&amp;#34;] console.</description>
